item.title: Double Cut Pug Tour Download
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: This game uses the classic horizontal adventure gameplay, in which players control a cute and nerdy pug dog, this dog can have a magical ability, players need to use this ability to complete a variety of challenges, rich and varied levels will surely bring players a richer experience. “Double Cut Pug” Game Advantages. Find purple coins hidden in the level and use them to unlock more items. unlock different props in the game, which can help players pass levels easily.
